      <h2><a id="importantDates">Important Dates</a></h2>
      <hr>
      <ul>
	<li>Submission deadline: 6th, April (anywhere on earth)</li>
	<li>Author notification: 4th, June</li>
	<li>Camera-ready for draft proceedings: 1st, July</li>
	<li>Early registration deadline: 10th, June </li>
	<li>Symposium: 9th-10th, July (Thursday/Friday)</li>
	<li>IJPP (HLPP special issue) submission deadline: 1st, October </li>
	<li>IJPP (HLPP special issue) camera-ready for journal
	  publication: 01st, December</li>
      </ul>	  
    </div>
  </section>



