	<a href="http://www.springer.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Springer</a> 
	in a special issue of the 
	<a href="http://www.springer.com/computer/theoretical+computer+science/journal/10766" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
	  International Journal of Parallel Programming</a>
	(IJPP).
